Wings Credit Union doing business as Ent Credit Union.

Please Note: If you have both a legacy Ent Credit Union and a legacy Wings Financial Credit Union share account(s), after June 30, 2026, the accounts will be aggregated into one account and will be insured up to a maximum amount of $250,000 under NCUAs share insurance.

Ent Credit Union has officially changed its name to Wings Credit Union. We will continue doing business as Ent Credit Union while we transition our branding to our new name.
